abstract: >-
  Living Board is a self-learning autonomous AI agent framework with
  dual-layer persistent memory (Supabase + Qdrant vector search),
  human-agent collaboration via a real-time dashboard, confidence-scored
  learnings with self-correction, and scheduled autonomous execution.
  The agent runs on an hourly loop, extracts knowledge from every cycle,
  and discovers cross-goal patterns through semantic similarity search.
